rface and implemented modern animations using <b>Emotion</b> and <b>Framer Motion</b> to ensure a consistent user experience across different devices.\",\"Configured an automated <b>CI/CD</b> workflow with <b>GitHub Actions</b> to deploy the application to <b>GitHub Pages</b>.\"],\"date\":[\"10/2023 - 11/2023\"]},{\"title\":\"Goose Track\",\"src\":\"https://nazarmural.github.io/goose-track-project/\",\"github\":\"https://github.com/acvetochka/goose-track-project\",\"technologies\":[\"React\",\"Redux Toolkit\",\"React Router\",\"Axios\",\"Trello\",\"Git\",\"GitHub\"],\"text\":[\"Full-Stack Team Project\",\"Role: Frontend Team Lead, Scrum Master, Frontend Developer.\"],\"description\":[\"Developed a responsive <b>React</b> web application for personal task and calendar management with <b>Google Authentication</b> as part of a full-stack team project.\",\"Implemented core monthly calendar functionality, including the user interface, interaction logic, and state management with <b>Redux Toolkit</b>, while collaborating closely with the backend team on <b>REST API</b> integration and issue resolution.\",\"Led a frontend <b>team of 9 developers</b>, conducted <b>Code Reviews</b>, and ensured consistent development standards and code quality.\",\"Served as <b>Scrum Master</b>, organizing the development workflow with <b>Trello</b>, facilitating <b>Agile ceremonies</b>, and coordinating collaboration across the frontend team.\"],\"date\":[\"09/2023 - 10/2023\"]},{\"title\":\"Phonebook\",\"src\":\"https://acvetochka.github.io/Phonebook/\",\"github\":\"https://github.com/acvetochka/Phonebook\",\"technologies\":[\"React\",\"Redux Toolkit\",\"Axios\",\"Node.js\",\"Express\",\"MongoDB\",\"REST API\",\"DigitalOcean\"],\"text\":[\"Full-Stack App\"],\"description\":[\"Developed a responsive contact management web application using <b>React</b> and <b>Redux Toolkit</b> with an intuitive and user-friendly interface.\",\"Designed and implemented a <b>RESTful API</b> using <b>Node.js</